      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 1118: In the ENABLE_PLUGIN-disabled path, edit updates emit the parent message without injectEditionOverwrites(), while the no-handler ENABLE_PLUGIN path does inject edition overwrite fields. If a build/runtime transition leaves local pluginData in memory, or if this helper becomes used independently of plugin availability, clients receive different edition shapes depending on compile flags. Keep the signal payload construction consistent by using injectEditionOverwrites() in both paths.",
      "revId": "1988cfe0f995f80694f069557c5397f9a68462b3",
